Test Case 2 – Login → Perform Action → Logout

Test Objective:
Verify that a logged-in user can access and view products before logging out.

Test Steps:

    Open the website https://automationexercise.com/

    Click Signup / Login and log in with valid credentials.

    After login, click on the Products tab.

    Verify that the “All Products” page is displayed.

    Click on any product to view details.

    Verify that product details (name, price, description) are visible.

    Click on Logout from the top menu.

    Verify that user is redirected to the login page.

Expected Result:
User should be able to log in, view product details, and log out successfully.